NOTICE OF DEFAULT AND ELECTION TO SELL
WARNING! IF YOU FAIL TO PAY THE
AMOUNTSPECIFIED IN THIS NOTICE YOU
COULD LOSE YOUR HOME, EVEN IF THE
AMOUNT IS IN DISPUTE!
TO:
DOC #956807
Official Records Nye County NV
Deborah Beatty - Recorder
06/02/2021 09:59:49 AM
Requested By: PACIFIC COAST TITLE
Recorded By: vw-RPTT:$0
Recording Fee: $37.00
Non Conformity Fee: $
Page 1 of 3
YOLANDA REYES NARCISO and LISBETH ALCANTARA
Pursuant to NEVADA REVISED STATUTES,
COMSTOCK PARK HOMEOWNERS' ASSOCIATION
does hereby give you NOTICE OF YOUR DEFAULT, AND DOES HEREBY ELECT TO SELL,
OR CAUSE THE SALE, to satisfy the obligation owing and arising out of your failure to pay your
Homeowners Assessments.
The LIEN of COMSTOCK PARK HOMEOWNERS' ASSOCIATION
recorded December 2, 2020, as Document No. 943146, in the Office of County Recorder of Nye
County, State of Nevada, securing the obligation of the assessments which was a deficiency in the
sum of $2,950.00, as of the date of the LIEN, PLUS ACCRUING ASSESSMENTS SINCE THAT
TIME, INTEREST, COSTS, and ATTORNEYS FEES or FEES of the AGENT for the
MANAGEMENT BODY,
The TOTAL DUE AS OF THIS DATE is $3,435.64, PLUS COSTS, and ATTORNEYS FEES or
FEES of the AGENT for the MANAGEMENT BODY. To find out the amount you must pay, or
arrange for payment to stop the foreclosure, or if your property is in foreclosure for any other
reason, contact HOA Collections LLC/
PURSUANT TO NEVADA REVISED STATUTES, the SALE will be held if this obligation is not
completely satisfied, and paid within NINETY (90) DAYS from the day of recording of this
NOTICE OF DEFAULT AND ELECTION TO SELL, on the real property described as follows:
Lot
21
Block
4
of
CALVADA VALLEY UNIT NO. 8A
as shown on the map thereof recorded April 5, 1971, in the Office of the County
Recorder of Nye County, State of Nevada under Document No. 23255.
Commonly known as: 290 W. Duck Creek Road, Pahrump, NV 89048
DATED: May 20, 2021
NOTARY: PLEASE SEE ATTACHED EXHIBIT "A"
